<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Appointment Cancellation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #fff5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #f5c2c7;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #ffe3e3;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #d32f2f;
    }
    .appointment-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .appointment-details td {
      padding: 5px 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Appointment Cancellation</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>

    <p>We regret to inform you that your appointment has been cancelled. Here are the details:</p>

    <table class="appointment-details">
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Appointment ID:</strong></td>
        <td><%= appointmentId %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Date:</strong></td>
        <td><%= date %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Time:</strong></td>
        <td><%= time %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Purpose:</strong></td>
        <td><%= purpose %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Contact:</strong></td>
        <td><%= contact %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Email:</strong></td>
        <td><%= email %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>If this was a mistake or you need to reschedule, please contact us.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company Team. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
